long.ar,de,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,es,es_419,fr,:
Your personal New Tab. Custom folders, custom bookmarks for work and for web surfing!

Easy switch between folders with different sets of your important bookmarks, so you can create new folder for your new opportunity, for example if you plan some jorney or travel you can create a folder and put in it many bookmarks associated with this jorney. 

Also you can use it like regular new tab with few most often used web links.


By clicking "Add to chrome" you accept and agree to installing "IQ Tab - Custom New Tab" extension and setting Chrome New Tab to that provided by the service and the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy. The extension will update your search settings and will change your search engine to be powered by Bing.

long.am,bg,bn,cs,da,el,et,fa,fi,fil,gu,hi,hr,:
Chrome tab audio manipulation channel.

Features:
- Volume control (up to 400% boost). 
- Audio Limiter / Compressor.
- 32hz-16khz Equalizer (includes popular presets). 
- Stereo/Mono toggle.
- Stereo/Mono Pan.
- SFX: Chorus, Reverb, Pitch shift.
- Karaoke mode.
- Save your own presets.
long.ca:
Ecualizador de pestañas de Chrome con presets populares, control de volumen, efectos de sonido y compresor de audio.

caracteristicas:
- Control de volumen (incluido el aumento por encima del valor predeterminado máximo).
- Limitador de audio / compresor.
- EQ - 32 a 16khz.
- Interruptor estéreo / mono.
- Pan estéreo.
- SFX: Chorus, Reverb, Pitch-Shift.
- Modo Karaoke
- Guarda tus propios presets personales.
